'''epoxide'''

#{{chemistry}} a [[class]] of [[organic]] [[compound]], [[cyclic]] [[ether]]s, having a three-membered [[ring]]; they are prepared by the selective [[oxidation]] of [[alkene]]s or by ring-closure of [[halohydrin]]s; used to make [[plastic]]s

====Synonyms====
*[[alkylene oxide]]

====Derived terms====
*[[epoxidation]]
*[[epoxidisable]], [[epoxidizable]]
*[[epoxidise]], [[epoxidize]]

